data.comment: The match is underway at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
Corner awarded to Tosu.
In the minute 3, Eduardo (Tosu) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Tosu have been awarded a corner by Akihiko Ikeuchi.
Can Tosu get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Cerezo's half?
In the minute 5, Throw-in high up the field for Tosu in Tosu.
Tosu have been awarded a corner by Akihiko Ikeuchi.
Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a Tosu throw-in in Cerezo's half.
In the minute 6, Goal kick for Cerezo at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 9, Jin Hyeon Kim has recovered and rejoins the match in Tosu.
The match at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium has been interrupted briefly for a check on Jin Hyeon Kim, who is down injured.
Cerezo are caught offside.
Throw-in Cerezo.
In the minute 14, Cerezo's Yuta Toyokawa breaks free at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium. But the strike goes wide of the post.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Tosu.
Corner awarded to Tosu.

In Tosu a free kick has been awarded the away team.

Akihiko Ikeuchi awards Cerezo a goal kick.
Hiroshi Kiyotake of Cerezo gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 21, Tosu have a goal kick.
Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a free kick to Tosu.
Tosu's Teruki Hara gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Cerezo defender.

Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
Free kick for Cerezo in the half of Tosu.
In the minute 27, Ball goes out of play for a Tosu goal kick.
Cerezo advance rapidly upfield but Akihiko Ikeuchi blows for offside.
Cerezo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 33, Tosu drive upfield and Yuto Uchida gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Cerezo defender.
Tosu have a dangerous throw-in.
Throw-in for Tosu in the half of Cerezo.
In the minute 39, Corner awarded to Cerezo.
Cerezo are pushing forward but Riku Matsuda's finish is wide of the goal.
Tosu have a goal kick.
In the minute 40, Throw-in for Cerezo at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Tosu.
Tosu are coming forward and Riki Harakawa gets in a strike, it misses the target, however.
In the minute 43, Ball goes out of play for a Cerezo goal kick.
Attention is being given to Cerezo’s Yoichiro Kakitani and play has been suspended briefly.
Cerezo to take a throw-in in Tosu territory.
In the minute 45, Yoichiro Kakitani returns to the field for Cerezo after picking up a slight injury.
The fourth official's board shows 4 minutes, which will be added to the 1st half.
Tosu awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 45, In Tosu Tosu drive forward through Tomoya Koyamatsu. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Corner awarded to Tosu.
Tosu's Ryoya Morishita misses with an attempt on goal.
In the minute 45, Goal kick for Cerezo at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
Akihiko Ikeuchi blows to end the first-half.
The second-half has just kicked-off.
Ball safe as Cerezo is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Tosu will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Cerezo.
In the minute 46, Eiichi Katayama is replacing Yoichiro Kakitani for the away team.
In the minute 48, Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a free kick to Cerezo just outside Tosu's area.
Throw-in for Cerezo in their own half.
Can Cerezo get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Tosu's half?
In the minute 50, Akihiko Ikeuchi awards Tosu a goal kick.
Goal! Kaisei Ishii gives Tosu a 1-0 lead in Tosu.
That's a fine assist from Tomoya Koyamatsu.
In the minute 52, Cerezo have been awarded a corner by Akihiko Ikeuchi.
Can Cerezo capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Tosu's half?
Cerezo to take a throw-in in Tosu territory.
In the minute 55, Tosu's Kaisei Ishii gets his shot away but it misses the target.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Tosu.
Akihiko Ikeuchi awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 56, Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.

Corner awarded to Cerezo.

Corner awarded to Cerezo.

Free kick for Cerezo in their own half.

Throw-in for Cerezo in their own half.

Eduardo (Tosu) gets a yellow card.
Free kick Tosu.

Cerezo have a goal kick.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.

Goal kick for Tosu at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.

Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.

Hiroaki Okuno is on a sub for Hiroshi Kiyotake for Cerezo.
In the minute 73, The away team have replaced Yuta Toyokawa with Koji Suzuki. This is the third substitution made today by Miguel Angel Lotina.
Goal! Tatsuhiro Sakamoto equalizes to bring the score to 1-1.
In the minute 75, Koji Suzuki with an assist there.
Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a free kick to Tosu in their own half.
Yuta Koike (Cerezo) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 78, Cerezo awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Tosu in their own half.

Tosu drives forward and Yuta Higuchi gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Tosu have been awarded a corner by Akihiko Ikeuchi.

Tosu's Daichi Hayashi gets his shot away but it misses the target.

Throw-in for Cerezo in the half of Tosu.
Goal kick for Tosu at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
In the minute 86, Myung Hwi Kim is making the team's fourth substitution at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium with Renzo Lopez replacing Yohei Toyoda.
Myung Hwi Kim (Tosu) is making a fifth substitution, with Ryang Yong-Gi replacing Eduardo.
Throw-in for Cerezo at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
In the minute 87, Free kick for Tosu in the half of Cerezo.
Akihiko Ikeuchi awards the away team a throw-in.
Throw-in for Cerezo at Ekimae Real Estate Stadium.
5 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
Tosu have a goal kick.
Akihiko Ikeuchi signals a free kick to Cerezo in their own half.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Tosu.
Ball safe as Tosu is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Tosu have been awarded a corner by Akihiko Ikeuchi.
Tosu drive upfield and Teruki Hara gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Cerezo defender.
Akihiko Ikeuchi awards the away team a throw-in.
Cerezo awarded a throw-in in their own half.
The second-half is over. The match ends 1-1.
